            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">[December 1860] ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to request in the name of the Board of Governors of the Botanic Gardens Adelaide, that you will please to inform me by post at your earliest convenience, as...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">60.12.00d</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Francis</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">GRG/70/1/1 Letter book of the Botanic Gardens Committee, State Records, South Australia.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>[December 1860]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">need to check date - two other items on same page are dec but not clear what year - subsequent items in p/c collection at MEL suggest date of 1860.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to request in the name of the Board of Governors of the Botanic Gardens Adelaide, that you will please to inform me by post at your earliest convenience, as follows</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>On what days of the week and what hours of the day are the Gardens at __________ open to the public, and if your garden be only open during certain days and hours — what is the reason that the attendance is confined to such times</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">I am Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>&amp;c &amp;c</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[G. W. Francis]</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
